title: hUC-MSC-exosome-1
source_name_ch1: human umbilical cord mesenchymal stem cells
extract_protocol_ch1: Exosomes were purified with total exosomes extraction kit for cell (introgen). The total RNA was extracted by seramir exosome RNA amplication kit (SBI).
extract_protocol_ch1.1: The RNA libraries were prepared with Small RNA Sample Pre Kit.
description: total RNA extracted from  none treated human umbilical cord mesenchymal stem cells
data_processing: The original image data obtained from Illumina Novaseq sequencing was converted into sequence data by Base Calling (FASTQ format) to obtain the most original sequencing data file.The FASTQ format file records the base and mass fraction of the read segment tested.FASTQ format is stored as sequence reads and each read has four lines. The first and third lines are composed of sequence identifiers and read names (the first line starts with '@' and the third line starts with '+').In the third line, ID can be omitted, but "+" cannot be omitted), the second behavior base sequence, and the sequencing mass fraction of the corresponding position of the fourth behavior base.
data_processing.2: Supplementary_files_format_and_content: Excel table with raw small RNA readcounts and transcripts per million for every small RNA.
contact_institute: Third affiliated hospital of sun yat-sen unversity
